de.feig.FEDM.Core

Interface INotificationListener


  • public interface INotificationListener
    This interface provides event signaling from this package to an application. Description:
    Interface for providing a listener interface for application classes, handling notification mode data

      • onNewNotification

        void onNewNotification(int error,
                       java.lang.String remoteIP,
                       int portNr)
        Listener method for the transponder data comming with notification event.
        Parameters:
        error -
        • 0 if OK
        • < 0 error code
        • > 0 status byte of the responded protocol, if the Reader signals a problem. See Reader's System Manual for the full list with all status bytes
        remoteIP - IP-Address of the reader
        portNr - port number of the local port which has received the notification
